title: custart tart/flan pâtissier recipe
description: im still polishing the recipe so it could be better
---
§recipe
	§ingredients
		§l [/recipes/pate_brisee.html] 1 pâte brisée §/l
		175g sugar
		4 eggs
		2 egg yolks
		800ml milk
		200ml cream
		90g cornstarch
		around 1tsp vanilla extract, can be replaced with vanilla sugar
	§/ingredients

	§instructions
		boil the milk and cream with the vanilla
		while its heating up mix the sugar and cornstarch
		add in the eggs and yolks and whisk
		add in the hot milk while still whisking
		then put it back in the pan and cook on low heat while still whisking for around 5 minutes until it gets a nice creamy thick consistency
		pour the cream in the dough and bake it at 180°c for 40 minutes
	§/instructions
§/recipe
